My theory (im not a manga reader)

The demon that Master Muzan kept alive has the Blood Demon Art to make people fall deep asleep in their dreams.
Inosuke, Tanjiro, Zeintsu and the Hashira, fall into the dream, and in order to wake up they have to cut something, but the dream doesnt just cointain that, it brings them back into the things they wish they can have, Tanjiro meets his family, Zeintsu has Nezuko as his waifu, Inosuke wishes he can be the Lord of the Ocean (i dont know), and idk about the Hashira.
Bruh if this is right I swear-
